OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and damp start for
OL,6,Fmost, though it will brighten up as
OL,7,Fthe day progresses, with some warm
OL,8,Fspells of sunshine developing.
OL,9,FHowever, a band of heavy rain will
OL,10,Falso push eastwards, with heavy
OL,11,Fshowers following from the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy rain quickly clearing
OL,14,Fto the east this evening, then a mix
OL,15,Fof clear spells and showers, these
OL,16,Fcontinuing overnight. Showers heaviest
OL,17,Fand most frequent in the northwest.
OL,18,FStaying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
