OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright and breezy day,
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers. Showers
OL,7,Fmost frequent in the north, some heavy
OL,8,Fwith the risk of hail and thunder.
OL,9,FFeeling warm in the sunshine.
